    {
      "id": "S2D16_Q15",
      "topic": "Testifying as Expert Witness",
      "question": "You have been retained as an expert witness in a fraud case involving complex cryptocurrency transactions. During your deposition, opposing counsel asks you to explain your methodology for tracing the digital assets. Which of the following is the MOST appropriate way to respond?",
      "options": [
        "Refuse to answer, stating that your methodology is proprietary and constitutes a trade secret that you cannot disclose",
        "Provide a detailed explanation of your methodology, including the tools, techniques, and analytical procedures you used to reach your conclusions",
